{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"5ad3b942-0cac-4f79-9cd6-b133c3c65be6","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest compatibility bridge by default.**\n\nIn 3.x, the SDK still included the VSTest adapter so `vstest.console` could discover tests. Starting with 4.0, MSTest.Sdk targets **Microsoft.Testing.Platform exclusively** — the VSTest adapter is no longer bundled, which is why `vstest.console` finds zero tests.\n\nYou have two options:\n\n### Option 1 — Switch to the new runner (recommended)\nReplace `vstest.console` in your CI with:\n```bash\ndotnet test\n```\nModern `dotnet test` auto-detects Microsoft.Testing.Platform.\n\n### Option 2 — Re-enable the VSTest bridge\nAdd this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nThis restores the adapter so `vstest.console` works again, but it's a compatibility shim — Option 1 is the long-term path.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"9f03c083-8747-4097-a0e0-a2b13cb9d2c2","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a known breaking change in MSTest.Sdk. Starting with MSTest.Sdk 3.x, the SDK uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform (the new test platform) by default. However, there's a key change between versions regarding VSTest compatibility.\n\nIn MSTest.Sdk 3.x, the VSTest adapter/runner bridge was still included by default, so `vstest.console` could still discover and run tests. Starting with MSTest.Sdk 4.0, the VSTest compatibility layer was removed by default — the SDK now exclusively targets Microsoft.Testing.Platform and no longer ships the VSTest adapter bridge unless you explicitly opt in.\n\n\nThis means `vstest.console.exe` can no longer discover or run tests with the newer SDK versions. To fix this, you can either migrate to `dotnet test` which uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform by default, or re-enable the VSTest bridge by adding a project file property that restores compatibility with the old test runner.","outputTokens":589,"requestId":"4C1C:39B23B:CEEAA3:FA5664:6A01488B"},"id":"f24a3c12-7813-42a3-971a-2839064ee880","timestamp":"2026-05-11T03:10:18.197Z","parentId":"4ee5b64d-dfd8-464a-8de4-4ea19b43a838"}
